## 1. Стек и bootstrap

### Технологический стек

| Concern | Выбор |
|---|---|
| Framework | **Angular 19** (standalone components, signals) |
| Language | **TypeScript** (strict mode) |
| Build | **Angular CLI** (`@angular/build`, esbuild-based) |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS 4** + CSS custom properties |
| Server state | **TanStack Query** (`@tanstack/angular-query-experimental`) |
| UI state | **NgRx Signal Store** (`@ngrx/signals`) |
| Grid | **AG Grid Community** (`ag-grid-angular`) |
| Routing | **Angular Router** (lazy loading, guards) |
| Icons | **Lucide Angular** (`lucide-angular`) |
| i18n | **@ngx-translate/core** |
| WebSocket | **@stomp/rx-stomp** |
| Date | **date-fns** |
| CDK | **@angular/cdk** (overlay, drag-drop, a11y) |

### Bootstrap

Приложение запускается через `bootstrapApplication(AppComponent, appConfig)` — **без NgModule**.

`appConfig` определяет providers:
- `provideRouter(routes, withComponentInputBinding())`
- `provideHttpClient(withInterceptors([authInterceptor]))`
- `provideAnimations()`
- `provideAngularQuery(new QueryClient({ ... }))`
- `importProvidersFrom(TranslateModule.forRoot({ ... }))`

```typescript
// ✅ app.config.ts — единая точка конфигурации
export const appConfig: ApplicationConfig = {
  providers: [
    provideRouter(routes, withComponentInputBinding()),
    provideHttpClient(withInterceptors([authInterceptor])),
    provideAngularQuery(new QueryClient({
      defaultOptions: {
        queries: { staleTime: 30_000, retry: 1 },
      },
    })),
    // ...
  ],
};
```

### Запрещено

- `NgModule` — не используются. Всё через standalone components + providers.
- `platformBrowserDynamic().bootstrapModule()` — устаревший подход.
- SSR / Angular Universal — не используется, это SPA.

