## 16. Naming conventions

### Файлы

| Тип | Паттерн | Пример |
|---|---|---|
| Component | `kebab-case.component.ts` | `connections-page.component.ts` |
| Service | `kebab-case.service.ts` | `connection-api.service.ts` |
| Guard | `kebab-case.guard.ts` | `auth.guard.ts` |
| Interceptor | `kebab-case.interceptor.ts` | `auth.interceptor.ts` |
| Model | `kebab-case.model.ts` | `connection.model.ts` |
| Store | `kebab-case.store.ts` | `workspace-context.store.ts` |
| Pipe | `kebab-case.pipe.ts` | `relative-time.pipe.ts` |
| Routes | `kebab-case.routes.ts` | `settings.routes.ts` |
| Test | `*.spec.ts` | `auth.service.spec.ts` |

### Классы

| Тип | Суффикс | Пример |
|---|---|---|
| Component | `*Component` | `ConnectionsPageComponent` |
| Service (API) | `*ApiService` | `ConnectionApiService` |
| Service (UI) | `*Service` | `ToastService`, `DetailPanelService` |
| Guard | `*Guard` (functional: `*Guard` variable) | `authGuard` |
| Store | `*Store` | `WorkspaceContextStore` |
| Pipe | `*Pipe` | `RelativeTimePipe` |
| Interceptor | `*Interceptor` (functional) | `authInterceptor` |

### Selectors

`dp-kebab-case` — с prefix `dp-`:

| Тип | Selector |
|---|---|
| Page component | `dp-connections-page` |
| Shared component | `dp-status-badge`, `dp-confirmation-modal` |
| Shell component | `dp-shell`, `dp-top-bar`, `dp-activity-bar` |
| Layout component | `dp-viewport-guard`, `dp-centered-content` |

### Методы

| Контекст | Паттерн |
|---|---|
| CRUD | `create*`, `update*`, `delete*`, `list*`, `get*` |
| UI actions | `open*`, `close*`, `toggle*`, `start*`, `cancel*` |
| Form | `submit*`, `reset*`, `isFormValid` |
| Event handlers | `on*` в template → метод без prefix в TS: `(click)="startCreate()"` |
| Formatters | `format*` — `formatDate`, `statusLabel`, `statusColor` |

